The steps are:

Import the necessary modules, including Selenium, ChromeDriverManager, LinkedinEasyApply, and YAML.

Define a method to initialize the Chrome webdriver with options to improve performance and compatibility.

Define a method to validate the input parameters from the configuration file.

Define a method to login to LinkedIn using the provided credentials.

Define a method to perform a customizable job search on LinkedIn using the LinkedinEasyApply module.

Define a method to apply to jobs on LinkedIn using the LinkedinEasyApply module.

Define the main method that will execute the job scraper.
